Name: UCSB
Description: One of the top Universities in California. Located along the Beach!

Name: Santa Barbara Cold Spring Tavern
Description: Beautiful restaurant up the mountains in Santa Barbara with beautiful scenery.

Name: Grand Canyon National Park
Description: One of themost profound parks in the US! Visitors have many ways of experiencing the Grand Canyon such as biking, hiking and even boating!

Name: Six Flags Magic Mountain
Description: A theme park in Santa Clarita with a handful of iconic rollercoaster rides. Also holds the world record for most rollercoaster rides in an amusement park!

Name: Las Vegas
Description: Located In the desert of Nevada with extremely hot summers and freezing cold winters. Las Vegas is one of the most worldwide tourist attractions because of its lively and and colorful night life.

Name: Griffith Observatory
Description: An observatory in Los Angeles where visitors can look through giant telescopes and visually connect with the cosmos.
